title: Ep. 1315 - Daya To Help Sunder - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya assures Sunder that she will help him out. Daya asks everyone to join her in this as she won't be able to him all alone. She suggests them to dance as the dancers didn't turn up. All except for Jetha agrees with Daya.

title: Ep. 1316 - Police Stops The Jalsa - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Pandey enters Gokuldham and asks them to stop the Jalsa party at once. He asks about the organiser but Sunder is nowhere to be found. Pandey threatens Jetha to put him behind bars. Gokuldham residents try to convince the police.

title: Ep. 1317 - Babita Looks For Iyer - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita is on the stage and is looking for Iyer. Iyer is busy looking for his costume. Meanwhile, Jethalal decides to dance with Babita. Taarak tells Jetha as how cunning Sunder is.

title: Ep. 1318 - Champaklal Dances With Tapu Sena - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Gokuldham is all praises for Champaklal's energy and dance style. Babita appreciates Sunderlal's efforts. Sunder offers money to Bhide as he danced brilliantly but he refuses to take. He says he wants to contribute 10% of his profit to the society.

title: Ep. 1319 - Bhide Plans Against Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide waits for the right moment to teach Jetha a lesson. Jetha gets in conversation with Babita, Iyer and Popatlal. Bhide calls him irresponsible and he asks for the reason. He reminds him about the maintenance which he has not paid yet.

title: Ep. 1320 - Bagha Is In Trouble Again - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha finds Bagha standing in the middle of the road. He asks him the reason to which he responds that he has no idea how he is standing there. Jetha takes him to the shop before he decides to stand still again.

title: Ep. 1321 - Bhide Has A Complain - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bhide tells Champaklal that he asked about the maintenance to Jetha to which he gave him a pressure cooker instead. He informs Daya that Bagha had come to deliver the pressure cooker.

title: Ep. 1322 - The Confusion Of Pressure Cooker - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya informs Jetha that he has given the pressure cooker along with the amount. Champaklal scolds him, Jetha tries to defend himself. Jetha requests Mauji not to reveal about the huge amount of money that he has given them.

title: Ep. 1323 - Haathi Examines Bagha - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Haathi examines Bagha and checks his eyes but to his surprise, there was no sign of any disease. Haathi tells Komal that Bagha might be going through some kind of trauma for which his behavior is changed.

title: Ep. 1324 - Baawri's Proposal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Bagha tells Daya about the Jalsa night and narrates about what had happened while they were returning back home. Baawri asks Bagha if she could walk him home. Baawri proposes Bagha and expresses her love for him.

title: Ep. 1325 - Bagha Is In Love - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha informs Nattu kaka about all the losses occurred due to Bagha's carelessness. Nattu kaka is rather happy for Bagha and encourages him. Daya calls Jetha up and asks him to lend some money to Bagha as he would be expressing his love to Baawri.

title: Ep. 1326 - Bagha's New Look - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Mauji overhears Champaklal's words and tells them that he has come to return the hefty amount. Baawri comes to Gada house and requests Bagha to come inside. Everyone is shocked to see the new look of Bagha.

title: Ep. 1327 - Daya Warns Jethalal - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Daya tries waking up Jetha and warns him that Champaklal would be back anytime soon. Champaklal comes and asks for Jetha. Abdul gets the Ayurvedic oil for Chacha ji. Jetha complains about the food.

title: Ep. 1328 - Jethalal's Resolution - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Babita asks Jetha to keep his resolution and start exercising from the next day. Daya is shocked to hear this and reveals his day's food plan. Jetha encourages Babita to help him with the yoga and exercises.

title: Ep. 1329 - Popatlal Is Unhappy With The Decision - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
shortDesc: Jetha calls up Babita and thanks her for the idea of setting up a fitness camp. Popatlal is not happy with the decision and asks Bhide to put this notice off the board. Upon hearing, Tapu Sena gets excited about the fitness camp.
